cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.DM, cs.CC, cs.SI. 

The paper deals with a search problem in which tests are performed on subsets of a given set, which is a common topic in information theory (cs.IT), data structures (cs.DS), and combinatorics (cs.DM). The paper also introduces new variants of cover-free families, which are relevant to coding theory (cs.CC) and information retrieval (cs.SI).
